\section{Unit Testing} % (fold)
\label{sec:unit_testing}

RBloomberg uses the RUnit package for testing. Tests can be found in inst/runit-tests. A test suite is defined in the file test.helper.R as follows:

<%= lidio("../../pkg/R/test.helper.R") %>

Tests can be run with a HTML report by running the file run.tests.R in the runit-tests directory:

<%= lidio("../../pkg/inst/runit-tests/run.tests.R") %>

More unit tests are always welcome and they can be added to one of the existing files or by creating a new file named according to the convention *Test.R.

There should not be any errors or failures when running the test suite.

